sentences.sentence: No time, I have to intubate.
sentences.translation: 没时间了，我得马上插管了。

sentences.sentence: It's hard to intubate. You want me to do that?
sentences.translation: 很难插管的，你要让我来做吗？

sentences.sentence: Side effects include apnea... be prepared to intubate your neonate!
sentences.translation: 这个药物的副作用包括呼吸暂停…准备给你的新生儿插管！
